snippet.title: Introducing Valiant Effort
snippet.description:
Valiant Effort will be coming to PC in 2020. Experience what it was like as an air crew over the dark skies of Occupied Europe. 

Visit our website here: https://www.valianteffortgame.com

Please join our Discord community here: https://discord.gg/wcY6A4g

Follow us on Twitter here: https://twitter.com/Valiant_Effort_

June 6, 1944 02:08 am - RAF Middleton St. George - Seven Lancaster bomber aircraft of 419 "Moose" Squadron form up on the taxiway and prepare for take-off. They hurtle down the runway at full throttle, barely cresting the treeline with a full bomb load. The target: Longues coastal battery on the Normandy coast, that has both Omaha and Gold beaches within range of the massive guns.
